Package: SVMFeature
Type: Package
Language: en-US
Title: Multiobjective Feature Selection Tools for Support Vector Machines
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Provides tools for feature selection in support vector machine models using the Non-dominated Sorting Genetic Algorithm II (NSGA-II). The package includes utilities for preprocessing, representation of candidate solutions, and multi-objective optimization of feature subsets for classification tasks. The implemented optimization strategy is based on Deb et al. (2002) <doi:10.1109/4235.996017>, and adapted by Alcaraz (2024) <doi:10.1016/j.cor.2024.106821> and Valero-Carreras et al. (2023) <doi:10.1016/j.cor.2022.106131>.
